merchant.name: Gado & Grill - One Raffles Place
merchant.description:
Gado & Grill offers some of the best Indonesian Cuisine serving a tantalising collection of dishes that are suitable for family, large groups, catching up with friends and colleagues. From Grilled Fish to Gado Gado, its extensive menu is reflective of the restaurant's effort to cater to every palate. This restaurant is located in One Raffles Place along Raffles Place. Gado & Grill is an ideal place where diners can enjoy delicious dishes in a casual and relaxed atmosphere that will surely deliver a memorable dining experience and gastronomic indulgence. MUST TRY: Indulge in their mouth-watering dishes such as Ayam Penyet, Grilled Chicken, Chunky Satay and Penyet Balls. 
Source: hungrygowhere.com

items.name: GadoMie™
items.description: Extremely popular, a twist of popular Indonesian indomie mi goreng with our very own chunky satay™ and crackers, choice of drinks available.

items.name: Gado Gado
items.description: Salad dish consisting of boiled vegetables, hard boiled eggs, beancurd, bean sprouts, and rice cake, served with peanut sauce dressing, and crackers, choice of drinks available.

items.name: Balanced Gado Set Meal
items.description:
Indonesian Gado-Gado with Chicken Satay. A balance and satisfying set meal
Set meal comes with a drink

items.name: NasiGo™
items.description:
Indonesian loves fried rice. We make it our way
Set meal comes with a drink

items.name: Ayam Penyet
items.description: Smashed fried chicken served with rice, crunchy flakes, beancurd, crackers, and hot chilli, choice of drinks available.

items.name: Ayam Bakar
items.description: Quarter chicken grilled with Indonesian sweet soya sauce, served with rice, beancurd, and crackers, choice of drinks available.

items.name: Bawal Bakar
items.description: Golden pomfret marinated with Gado & Grill special bbq dressing and Indonesian sweet soya sauce, and then grilled to perfection. Set meal comes with warm white rice, a choice of drink and Keropok King vegetable crackers.

items.name: Bakso Penyet
items.description: Bakso penyet is served using our 'the best Indonesian beef ball made in Singapore', coated with the penyet flour and then deep fried to perfection. Set meal comes with warm white rice, a choice of drink and Keropok King vegetable crackers.
